data.name: WrapInfluenceOnPosition
desc: These values specify the influence of the wrapping style of a floating screen object when it's positioned.

items.name: ONCE_SUCCESSIVE
lines: wrapping style has no influence on the position and the floating screen object is successive positioned.

items.name: ONCE_CONCURRENT
lines: wrapping style has no influence on the position and the floating screen object is concurrent positioned.

items.name: ITERATIVE
lines: wrapping style has influence on the position and the floating screen object is iterative positioned.
